/DG9L5sUJyPv/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.libeautymedspa.com/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://classpass.nz/studios/l-beauty-house-skincare-and-spa-houston?reviewsPage=1"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.instagram.com/li.beautyhouse/?hl=en"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.yelp.com/biz/glo-laser-and-med-spa-yujing-li-md-houston"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.facebook.com/libeautyhouse/about/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.yelp.com/biz/medispa-institute-houston"}]}},{"id":"ws_87ab2bf5-5a91-9ab5-86a6-c468c9209594_call-12032cc0-1d23-4c56-b918-e223726d3a41-5","type":"web_search_call","status":"completed","action":{"type":"search","query":"Tu Es Belle Spa Houston reviews facial","sources":[{"type":"url","url":"https://www.yelp.com/biz/tu-es-belle-spa-bellaire"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.facebook.com/aestheticsbyrozmin/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.groupon.com/deals/tu-es-belle-spa-13?srsltid=AfmBOoq32eLLDxkbJGrlzdTWkZeiDWDTxoGlrCk0IZQ191R4TgIG8Xqm"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.tuesbellespa.com/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://reviews.birdeye.com/tu-es-belle-spa-169812307705868"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.groupon.com/deals/tu-es-belle-spa-26?srsltid=AfmBOorRgzu1FXYn1wlzZ2HLkeOICEkuqxNjnWB7EeiTmvQ7EPjhR9np"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.facebook.com/AestheticsDepartmentatTuEsBelleSpa/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.instagram.com/reel/DTZJsQ1jvg4/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.groupon.com/deals/tu-es-belle-spa-28?srsltid=AfmBOooMVe21JMw6UaK_7x0A_XNFgcSoizGwd9Iuew2pn_l0Q1eVxH4Z"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.facebook.com/893498664090953/"}]}},{"id":"tco_87ab2bf5-5a91-9ab5-86a6-c468c9209594_call-12032cc0-1d23-4c56-b918-e223726d3a41-4","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_87ab2bf5-5a91-9ab5-86a6-c468c9209594_call-12032cc0-1d23-4c56-b918-e223726d3a41-3","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_87ab2bf5-5a91-9ab5-86a6-c468c9209594_call-12032cc0-1d23-4c56-b918-e223726d3a41-5","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"content":[{"type":"output_text","text":"**Top recommendations for facial spas in West Houston (areas like Westchase, Memorial, West U/Rice Village, Katy/Energy Corridor) emphasize high ratings on Yelp/Google, specialization in facials/skincare, recent positive feedback, and convenient west-side locations.**[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facials+Spa&find_loc=Houston%2C+TX)[[2]](https://www.libeautymedspa.com/)\n\n### Standout Options\n- **Lì Beauty Medspa (Li Beauty House Medspa)** — 12110 Westheimer Rd, Houston, TX 77077 (Westchase/West Houston).  \n  This medical-grade spa specializes in facials, acne treatments, nano infusion, and advanced skincare with licensed estheticians. Reviewers highlight transformative results for skin issues like cystic acne, relaxing experiences (e.g., HydraFacials), and high-quality products/techniques. Strong ratings around 4.8–5.0 across platforms. Ideal for targeted, results-driven facials.[[3]](https://classpass.com/studios/l-beauty-house-skincare-and-spa-houston)[[2]](https://www.libeautymedspa.com/)\n\n- **Tu Es Belle Spa** — 333 West Loop North #410, Houston, TX 77024 (Memorial area).  \n  A boutique spot with a medical esthetician offering personalized treatments like HydraFacials, botanical facials, chemical peels, microneedling, and 24K Gold Leaf facials. Clients praise the professionalism, relaxing atmosphere, visible skin improvements, and tailored approach for concerns like acne or anti-aging. Good reviews for consistent quality.[[4]](https://www.tuesbellespa.com/)\n\n- **Dharma Skin Spa** — Houston Heights area (e.g., near 77006, often surfacing in west-side searches).  \n  Known for holistic, clean/natural product facials with excellent extractions and calming experiences. Yelp ratings around 4.8 with frequent praise for estheticians (e.g., Lindsey) and skin-nourishing results. A top-rated choice for those preferring gentle, wellness-focused treatments.[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facials+Spa&find_loc=Houston%2C+TX)[[5]](https://www.yelp.com/biz/dharma-skin-spa-houston)\n\n### Other Strong Contenders in/near West Houston\n- **Bare Necessities** (Tanglewood/Upper Kirby locations) — Highly rated (4.8 on Yelp) for comprehensive skincare and facials; convenient for west-central access.[[6]](https://www.houstoniamag.com/health-and-wellness/best-massage-facial-day-spas-houston)\n- **Spavia Cinco Ranch** or **MedSpa at Villagio** (Katy area) — Luxury day spa or medical spa options with facials, massages, and more; good for further-west visitors.[[7]](https://cincoranchtx.spaviadayspa.com/)[[8]](https://medspaatvillagio.com/)\n- **Hand & Stone** (Rice Village) — Affordable, consistent professional facials and massages in the West U area.[[9]](https://handandstone.com/locations/houston-rice-village/?srsltid=AfmBOooRvzMFdGh8o5ftM5TZzeHzwlM1dnQceX7VNd9VIiG_CLt_LQTi)\n\n### Quick Tips\nRatings and popularity come from recent Yelp, Google, and review aggregators (as of 2026 data). “Best” depends on your needs (e.g., acne vs. relaxation, budget, or specific treatments like peels/microneedling)—check current availability, esthetician specialties, and reviews directly. Book via their sites or apps like Vagaro/ClassPass where mentioned. For the most up-to-date info, search Yelp/Google for “facials near [your zip]” or visit the spa websites.[[10]](https://m.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facials&find_loc=West+Houston%2C+TX)\n\nWest Houston options lean toward medical spas for advanced results or boutique spots for personalized care. Enjoy your treatment!","logprobs":[],"annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Facials+Spa&find_loc=Houston%2C+TX","start_index":268,"end_index":347,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.libeautymedspa.com/","start_index":347,"end_index":385,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://classpass.com/studios/l-beauty-house-skinca